casebody.data:
No. 108,

Orig.

Nebraska v. Wyoming et al. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 522 U. S. 1026.]

Motion of the Special Master for compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $98,644.56 to be paid as follows: 35% by Nebraska, 35% by Wyoming, 5% by Colorado, and 25% by the United States.
